snippet.title: Disney Emoji Blitz - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Collect and play with 400+ Disney and Pixar emojis to score big points and share in chat messages with friends!

Play fast paced rounds of match-3 to earn prizes, complete missions, and discover new emojis. Collect Disney and Pixar emoji characters and items from The Little Mermaid, The Lion King, Cinderella, Zootopia, The Muppets, Disney|Pixar's Toy Story, Monsters, Inc., Finding Dory and more!

Match. Collect. Emote!

Download today!
iOS: http://di.sn/6000BaCin
Android: http://di.sn/6006BaCmI
